<view class="full-report-page">
  <view class="page-scroll c10-report">
    <view class="c10-status">
      <text>9:41</text>
      <text>▰ wifi ▰</text>
    </view>

    <view class="c10-top">
      <button class="c10-back" bindtap="onReturnEntry" aria-label="返回">‹</button>
      <text class="c10-title">完整报告</text>
      <text class="c10-count">错题 1 / 8</text>
    </view>

    <view class="c10-hero">
      <view>
        <text class="c10-heading">AI 提分报告（完整）</text>
        <text class="c10-time">报告生成时间：2024-05-30 10:36</text>
        <view class="c10-score-card">
          <image class="c10-score-icon" src="/assets/icons/shield-check-purple-clean.png" mode="aspectFit" />
          <view>
            <text class="c10-score-label">可追回分数（可优先改善）</text>
            <view class="c10-score-line"><text>6-10</text><text>分 ↑</text></view>
            <text class="c10-score-note">通过优先修复关键错因，有机会追回的分数区间</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <image class="c10-owl c10-owl-core" src="/assets/icons/full-report-mascot.png" mode="aspectFill" />
      <image class="c10-owl c10-owl-v13" src="/assets/icons/v13-full-report-mascot.png" mode="aspectFill" />
    </view>

    <view class="c10-card c10-evidence">
      <view class="c10-card-head">
        <image class="c10-card-icon" src="/assets/icons/shield-check-purple-clean.png" mode="aspectFit" />
        <view>
          <text class="c10-card-title">证据锚点</text>
          <text class="c10-card-sub">本报告结论均基于事实题目分析</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="c10-table">
        <text>题号</text><text>学生答案</text><text>正确答案</text><text>错因依据</text>
        <text>二(1)</text><text>20 千米</text><text>45 千米</text><text>速度差 × 时间 计算错误</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="c10-card c10-priority">
      <view>
        <view class="c10-card-head tight">
          <image class="c10-card-icon" src="/assets/icons/target-purple-clean.png" mode="aspectFit" />
          <view>
            <text class="c10-card-title">提分优先级</text>
            <text class="c10-priority-title">行程问题中的数量关系建模</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <text class="c10-priority-copy">优先级依据：本次考试中该类问题失去 7 分，属于高频且可快速改善的题型。</text>
      </view>
      <image class="c10-target c10-target-core" src="/assets/icons/full-report-target.png" mode="aspectFill" />
      <image class="c10-target c10-target-v13" src="/assets/icons/v13-full-report-target.png" mode="aspectFill" />
    </view>

    <view class="c10-card c10-question-list core-only">
      <text class="c10-section-title">关键错题</text>
      <text class="c10-section-sub">建议优先修复 1-3 道</text>
      <view class="c10-question">
        <text class="c10-number">1</text>
        <view class="c10-question-body">
          <view class="c10-question-head"><text>二元一次方程应用题（行程问题）</text><text class="c10-badge red">未修复</text></view>
          <text class="c10-blue">可追回分数：2-3 分</text>
          <text>知识点：二元一次方程的应用-行程问题</text>
          <text>学生错误：速度单位换算错误，导致时间计算偏差</text>
          <text>错因：未理解“速度差 × 时间=路程差”模型</text>
          <button class="c10-fix" data-question-id="q1" bindtap="onOpenRepairDrawer">修复这道关键错题</button>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="c10-question second">
        <text class="c10-number">2</text>
        <view class="c10-question-body">
          <view class="c10-question-head"><text>一次函数图像与性质</text><text class="c10-badge red">未修复</text></view>
          <text class="c10-blue">可追回分数：1-2 分</text>
          <text>知识点：一次函数的图像与性质</text>
          <text>学生错误：截距理解偏差，图像平移方向错误</text>
          <button class="c10-fix" data-question-id="q2" bindtap="onOpenRepairDrawer">修复这道关键错题</button>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="c10-card c10-question-list writeback-only">
      <text class="c10-section-title">关键错题</text>
      <text class="c10-section-sub">建议优先修复 1-3 道</text>
      <view class="c10-question">
        <text class="c10-number">1</text>
        <view class="c10-question-body">
          <view class="c10-question-head"><text>二元一次方程应用题（行程问题）</text><text class="c10-badge green">已修复 / 初步掌握</text></view>
          <text class="c10-blue">可追回分数：2-3 分</text>
          <text>知识点：二元一次方程的应用-行程问题</text>
          <text>学生错误：速度单位换算错误，导致时间计算偏差</text>
          <text>错点：未理解“速度差 × 时间=路程差”模型</text>
          <button class="c10-fix" data-question-id="q1" bindtap="onOpenRepairDrawer">查看修复记录</button>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="c10-card c10-teacher">
      <image class="c10-card-icon" src="/assets/icons/shield-check-purple-clean.png" mode="aspectFit" />
      <view>
        <view class="c10-question-head"><text class="c10-card-title">老师介入判断</text><text class="c10-blue">查看判断依据 ›</text></view>
        <text class="c10-priority-title">暂不需要老师介入</text>
        <text class="c10-priority-copy">依据：关键错题验证通过，当前可先自主专项训练。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="bottom-actions c10-actions">
    <button class="outline-button" data-action="save-report" bindtap="onSaveReport">保存报告</button>
    <button class="outline-button share-action" data-action="share-report" bindtap="onShareReport">分享报告</button>
    <button class="solid-button" data-question-id="q1" bindtap="onOpenRepairDrawer">继续看下一部分 ›</button>
  </view>

  <view class="toast" wx:if="{{toast}}">{{toast}}</view>
</view>
